# KYC Copilot — Core Rule

## Session start
1. Read `docs/CONTEXT_INDEX.md`
2. Adopt role from matrix → `docs/roles/<ROLE>.md`
3. Run `docs/instructions/IS-001-session-bootstrap.md`
4. Load only files listed in CONTEXT_INDEX matrix for your task type

## Session end
Run `docs/instructions/IS-006-session-exit.md` → write `.session-state.yaml`

## Cite, don't explain
- Invariants: `INV-001`..`INV-007` (see `docs/ARCHITECTURE_CONTEXT.md` §8)
- Decisions: `ADR-001`..`ADR-009` (see `docs/DECISIONS.md`)

## Entry points
- Process: `src/index.ts`
- API: `src/api/index.ts`
- Graph: `src/graph/graph.ts`
- Worker: `src/workers/graph-runner.ts`
- Schema: `src/db/schema.ts`

## Verify before claiming done
`npm run typecheck && npm run test`
